2004-10-23 Dan Williams <dcbw@redhat.com>

	* info-daemon/NetworkManagerInfoDbus.c
		- Trap the "DeviceActivationFailed" signal

	* docs/NetworkManager DBUS API.txt
		- Add "DeviceActivationFailed" signal

